headline: Marsh McLennan Stockholders Re-Elect Board of Directors During 2025 Meeting
summary: NEW YORK, May 15, 2025--Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC), a global leader in risk, strategy, and people, today announced the results of its 2025 Annual Meeting of Stockholders.

headline: Marsh & Mclennan Companies, Inc. Announces Retirement of Oscar Fanjul from the Board
summary: Marsh & McLennan Companies, Inc. announced that Oscar Fanjul is retiring from the Board after more than 23 years of service and did not stand for re-election. Oscar Fanjul is retiring from the Board...
